# Prompt Pack Enforcement

When user intent is planning, building, or auditing, follow these prompt packs:

- `docs/prompt-packs/PLAN.md`
- `docs/prompt-packs/BUILD.md`
- `docs/prompt-packs/AUDIT.md`

## Required Output Structure

- List evidence files read.
- Identify API boundary entries used.
- Identify Trigger task entries used when async/integration scope exists.
- Include verification steps.

## Doc Sync Contract (Mandatory)

If code changes in session, update truth docs in same session:

- architecture/ownership -> `TRUTH_LAYER.md`, `project_state/engineering_map.yaml`
- behavior/journey -> `project_state/journeys.yaml`
- API boundary -> `docs/system_map/API_CATALOG.md`
- Trigger wiring -> `docs/system_map/TRIGGER_TASK_CATALOG.md`
- release verification policy -> `docs/RELEASE_GATE_CRITERIA.md`

Do not mark work complete if required doc updates are missing.
